{"tid":2198082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳彥霖死因研訊】裁判官引導陪審團裁決只能選「死於意外」或「死因存疑」","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:15:00.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"986f449b4ae412388eed50fd5deb0a730c4a418b","tid":2198082,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"職訓局青年學院 15 歲女生陳彥霖，去年 9 月赤裸浮屍油塘海面，死因裁判法庭經過 11 天研訊、傳召 32 位證人，死因裁判官高偉雄今（11 日）總結證供及引導陪審團，表明剔除「非法被殺」及「死於自殺」選項，陪審團可在「死於意外」或「死因存疑」兩個選項中達成裁決。陪審團聽畢總結後，下午退庭商議裁決。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官高偉雄今早表示，15 歲的彥霖在全身赤裸的情況下離世，是一件難過事情。他指由彥霖失蹤至發現屍體期間，沒有目擊證人，死因庭沒有直接證據，知道案發經過、如何導致死亡，故陪審團要作出一個推論。他說：「你們（陪審團）可以作出推論，不可以作出猜測。推論是根據證供，猜測則沒有任何證供作基礎。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%89%94%E9%99%A4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85-%E5%BC%95%E5%B0%8E%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA-%E6%AD%BB%E6%96%BC%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-%E6%88%96-%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E5%AD%98%E7%96%91/?fbclid=IwAR00wcmExjNVGUhkILgEyP-FwfU283Xj5WM01Bb0-ZsPj-EhFB-OgJSdaJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2589%2594%25E9%2599%25A4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E9%25A0%2585-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%25B1%25BA-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E6%2588%2596-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25AD%2598%25E7%2596%2591%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR00wcmExjNVGUhkILgEyP-FwfU283Xj5WM01Bb0-ZsPj-EhFB-OgJSdaJk&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=b5684a88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2599%25B